  "original_title": "\u0dbb\u0db1\u0dca\u0da2\u0db1\u0dca \u0dad\u0db1\u0dad\u0dd4\u0dbb \u0db6\u0dcf\u0dbb \u0d9c\u0db1\u0dd3",
  "text_idx": {
    "en": {
      "title": "Ranjan takes over the position",
      "author": "unknown",
      "body_lines": [
        "Mr. Ranjan Ramanayake assumed the position of ambassador for the welfare and promotion of expatriate workers.",
        "After receiving the presidential amnesty, the Minister of Labor and Foreign Employment Mr. Manusha Nanayakkara announced that Mr. Ranjan Ramanayake will be offered this position.",
        "Mr. Ranjan Ramanayake went to Madivela councilor's house where he used to reside the previous night with Mr. Manusha Nanayakkara and his supporters, where Mr. Manusha Nanayakkara officially offered the relevant position.",
        "Member of Parliament Mr. Wimalaweera Dissanayake also came to that event and said that he was happy that his neighbor was freed."
      ],
